Package: stevents
Title: Lightweight Classes for Spatio-Temporal Event Patterns
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ricardo", "Sales Piquer", , "ricardosalespiquer@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides simple S3 classes for representing spatio-temporal 
    event patterns and space-time tessellations. Designed as a small 
    preprocessing layer for spatio-temporal point process modelling, 
    with native support for 'sf' geometries.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
